summary: WHILE DRIVING THE VEHICLE STOPPED DEAD. IT WOULD NOT RESTART. HAD IT TOWED TO LOCAL DEALER. THE TIPM (TOTAL INTEGRATED POWER MODULE) AND BOTH FUEL PUMPS WERE OUT!  PART WAS BACK ORDERED FOR A MONTH.  I WAS WITHOUT MY VEHICLE ALMOST 4 WEEKS.  DROVE IT TWO DAYS ON A TRIP AND THE CONSTANT VELOCITY JOINT WENT OUT!  *TR
